ly reducing pending cases across the state.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/technology/haryana-launches-online-auto-mutation-system-to-combat-property-fraud/131081486?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-70908/131081486.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "technology"}]}